    content: "Thanks so much for coming #AloneTogether opening party at Little Creatures!! Let's take a look of some photos behind the scenes :) Great effort of Mateusz Kolek @mateusz_kolek and Storyteller team to set up the exhibition in 2 hours 🌝 Big thanks again to this wonderful restaurant along the sea. We had a very wonderful night !! The show will start tomorrow til Jun 9 at Storyteller Space - Cabinet of Stories at Central. Let’s be ALONE TOGETHER :) ·\n·\n波蘭插畫家Mateusz Kolek在香港的個人展覽「Alone Together: Mateusz Kolek」將自5月7日起至6月9日於@cabinet.of.stories 進行。\n·\n【展覽詳情】\n·\n展覽於兩個空間同時展出：\n·\n👉🏻Little Creatures : 一間來自澳洲位於海旁的酒吧餐廳，環境美麗提供偌大空間，畫作的大型版將會於這裡的牆上展出，開幕酒那晚餐廳還會暫停部分營業，特別騰出空間展出Mateusz 其他的亞洲系列作品。5月5日後，餐廳將回復正常營業，但牆上大型畫作仍照常展出。\n·\n👉🏻Cabinet of Stories: Storyteller 的實體故事館，除展出Mateusz 全新香港系列的作品，還有特別的聽故事體驗，參觀者可看著畫作戴上耳筒專心於一個人的空間聽每幅畫的故事。 · · 👀地點：Cabinet of Stories @cabinet.of.stories ·\n中環士丹頓街15號1樓 \nTue - Fri: 3pm - 7pm / Weekends: 2pm - 6pm\n·\n****展覽提示： -故事館參觀者最好請自備耳筒\n-故事館展覽開始日期為5月7日\n·\n👀地點：Little Creatures ·\n西環堅尼地城堅彌地城新海旁2-5A號五福大廈 地下1號舖\n· 【Exhibition Info】 👉🏻Little Creatures :\n\nSpecial thanks to this beautiful bar along the sea - Little creatures will offer the visitors free beer & snacks apart from the art space in the opening party 🙂 Artworks exhibiting on walls will continue till Jun9. 👉🏻Cabinet of Stories:\n\nStoryteller space of storytelling. In this space, apart from displaying the Hong Kong whole series of artworks, we have prepared a special experience of sound walk for the exhibition. Visitors can bring your earphones to listen to the story behind each of the art works. 👀Venue：Cabinet of Stories\n\n1/F, 15 Staunton Street, Central\n\nTue - Fri: 3pm - 7pm / Weekends: 2pm - 6pm ****Visitor tips： Bring your own earphones for the sound walk section 👀Venue：Little Creatures\n\nShop 1, G/F, New Fortune House, 2-5A New Praya, Kennedy Town, Western District\n\nLet's be ALONE TOGETHER!\n·\nPhoto by @liknifena",
