    _id: ObjectId("5d47cccf25ae2a0d783d414e"),
    "time_stamp": "2017--12--03 22:38:42",
    "imgs_url": "https://instagram.fhel5-1.fna.fbcdn.net/vp/250dc57d5ebec0574c11a48bb8351d11/5DD7EED1/t51.2885-15/e35/24273925_389235601497864_8944634745313034240_n.jpg?_nc_ht=instagram.fhel5-1.fna.fbcdn.net",
    content: "【#STORYTELLER現正尋找冬日戀愛故事】 “You are summer to my winter heart.” - Gemma Troy \n據說，冬天是個令人容易戀愛的季節，Storyteller現正尋找發生在冬日的戀愛故事，相愛、單戀、暗戀、苦戀⋯⋯在愛情故事裡，學習愛。我們將揀選精彩故事，為它畫上一幅插畫，讓故事留傳。請於12月15日前把故事傳至：info@story-teller.com.hk\n\nIllustration by @patpat_kate",
